sequenceDiagram
    actor Customer
    participant Yves as Yves Storefront
    participant Locator as Dealer Locator
    participant MR as Merchant Relationship<br>(B2B Contracts)
    actor Dealer as Dealer (Merchant Portal)
    participant Rest as Product Restrictions<br>+ Custom Prices
    participant OMS as Order / OMS

    Customer->>Locator: Find a dealer (linkout)
    Locator-->>Customer: Selected dealer
    Customer->>Yves: Send registration/join request
    Yves->>MR: Create contract request
    MR-->>Dealer: Appears in "new customers" overview
    Dealer->>MR: Accept + assign merchant-specific customer ID
    Dealer->>Rest: Configure prices/delivery + product visibility
    MR-->>Customer: Approved (added to dealer pool)

    Customer->>Yves: Select active dealer, browse
    Yves->>Rest: Resolve visible products + dealer/customer prices
    Rest-->>Yves: Dealer-scoped catalog + discount-group prices
    Customer->>Yves: Place order (Invoice)
    Yves->>OMS: Create merchant order
    OMS-->>Dealer: Order to fulfil & ship
    Note over Customer,Dealer: Dealer↔customer comments available on the order
